{"title_page": "2009 World Wrestling Championships \u2013 Women's freestyle 63 kg", "text_new": "{{2009 World Wrestling Championships}}\n{{main|2009 World Wrestling Championships}}\n\nThe '''women's freestyle 63&nbsp;kg''' is a competition featured at the [[2009 World Wrestling Championships]], and was held at the Messecenter Herning exhibition center in [[Herning Municipality|Herning]], [[Denmark]] on September 24.\n\n==Medalists==\n{|class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n|bgcolor=\"gold\"|'''Gold'''||{{flagmedalist|[[Mio Nishimaki]]|JPN}}\n|-\n|bgcolor=\"silver\"|'''Silver'''||{{flagmedalist|[[Lubov Volosova]]|RUS}}\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\" bgcolor=\"#cc9966\"|'''Bronze'''||{{flagmedalist|[[Yelena Shalygina]]|KAZ}}\n|-\n|{{flagmedalist|[[Justine Bouchard]]|CAN}}\n|}\n\n==Results==\n;Legend\n*'''F''' \u2014 Won by [[Pin (amateur wrestling)|fall]]\n\n===Final===\n\n{{2TeamBracket-Tennis3\n| seeds = no\n| RD1=Final\n| nowrap = no\n\n| team-width=205\n| score-width=15\n\n| RD1-team1='''{{flagathlete|[[Mio Nishimaki]]|JPN}}'''\n| RD1-score1-1='''1'''\n| RD1-score1-2='''8'''\n| RD1-score1-3=&nbsp;\n| RD1-team2={{flagathlete|[[Lubov Volosova]]|RUS}}\n| RD1-score2-1=0\n| RD1-score2-2=1\n| RD1-score2-3=&nbsp;\n}}\n\n===Top half===\n{{16TeamBracket-Compact-Wrestling\n| RD1=Round of 32\n| RD2=Round of 16\n| RD3=Quarterfinals\n| RD4=Semifinals\n\n| team-width=180\n| score-width=15\n\n| RD1-team15={{flagathlete|[[Hanna Belyaeva]]|BLR|1995}}\n| RD1-score15-1='''3'''\n| RD1-score15-2=3\n| RD1-score15-3=&nbsp;\n| RD1-team16='''{{flagathlete|[[Nikola Hartmann]]|AUT}}'''\n| RD1-score16-1=0\n| RD1-score16-2=2<sup>'''F'''</sup>\n| RD1-score16-3=&nbsp;\n\n| RD2-team01={{flagathlete|[[Zhao Junzhi]]|CHN}}\n| RD2-score01-1=0\n| RD2-score01-2=&nbsp;\n| RD2-score01-3=&nbsp;\n| RD2-team02='''{{flagathlete|[[Yuliya Tkach|Yuliya Ostapchuk]]|UKR}}'''\n| RD2-score02-1=4<sup>'''F'''</sup>\n| RD2-score02-2=&nbsp;\n| RD2-score02-3=&nbsp;\n\n| RD2-team03='''{{flagathlete|[[Yelena Shalygina]]|KAZ}}'''\n| RD2-score03-