V |url=https://pia.gov.ph/news/articles/1036790 |accessdate=March 31, 2020 |work=Philippine Information Agency |date=March 21, 2020 |language=en}}</ref><ref name=\"PNAGovPH-CovidWestVisayas\" />\n**[[Capiz]]<ref name=\"PNAGovPH-CovidWestVisayas\" />\n**[[Iloilo]]<ref name=\"PNAGovPH-CovidWestVisayas\" />\n**''[[Iloilo City]]''<ref name=\"PNAGovPH-CovidWestVisayas\" />\n**[[Negros Occidental]]<ref name=\"MB-CovidNegrosOcc\">{{cite news |last1=Masculino |first1=Glazyl |title=Negros Occ brgy declared \u2018hot zone\u2019 after 1st COVID-19 positive case |url=https://news.mb.com.ph/2020/03/29/negros-occ-brgy-declared-hot-zone-after-1st-covid-19-positive-case/ |accessdate=March 31, 2020 |work=Manila Bulletin |date=March 29, 2020}}</ref>\n*[[Central Visayas]] (Region VII)\n**[[Bohol]]<ref name=\"PNAGovPH-CovidBohol\">{{cite news |last1=Valencia |first1=Angeline |title=Bohol exec wants isolation area in every barangay |url=https://www.pna.gov.ph/articles/1098307 |accessdate=April 1, 2020 |work=Philippine News Agency |date=March 31, 2020 |language=en}}</ref>\n**[[Cebu]]<ref name=\"ABSCBN-CovidCebu\">{{cite news |title=Cebu records 1st case of COVID-19 |url=https://news.abs-cbn.com/news/03/18/20/cebu-records-1st-case-of-covid-19 |accessdate=March 31, 2020 |work=ABS-CBN News |date=March 18, 2020 |language=en}}</ref>\n**''[[Cebu City]]''<ref name=\"YahooPHNews-CovidCebuCity\">{{cite news |title=Cebu City \u2018now has 19 Covid cases\u2019 |url=https://ph.news.yahoo.com/cebu-city-now-19-covid-160400370.html |accessdate=March 31, 2020 |work=Yahoo! News Philippines |publisher=SunStar |date=March 29, 2020 |language=en-PH}}</ref>\n**''[[Lapu-Lapu, Cebu|Lapu-Lapu]]''<ref name=\"YahooPHNews-CovidCebuCity\" />\n**''[[Mandaue]]''<ref name=\"CNNPH-CovidMandaue\">{{cite news |title=COVID-19 reaches Cebu as Mandaue City confirms first case |url=http://www.cnnphilippines.com/regional/2020/3/18/Cebu-Mandaue-City-COVID-19-coronavirus.html |accessdate=March 31, 2020 |work=CNN Philippines |dat