gali language]] owned by [[Viacom 18]]. <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://dreamdth.com/threads/viacom-18-to-launch-soon-colors-bangla-cinema-by-rename-the-office-channel.116729/|title=DDF Exclusive - Viacom 18 To Launch Soon \"Colors Bangla Cinema\" by Rename \"The Office\" Channel|website=DreamDTH - Technology Discussion Forums|language=en-US|access-date=2019-03-18}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.viacom18.com/on-air/regional/colors-bangla|title=Colors Bangla Cinema}}</ref>\n\n[https://www.thakumarjhuli.in Bangla movie download]\n\n== References ==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{Bengali-language television channels}}\n\n[[Category:Bengali-language television channels in India]]\n[[Category:Television stations in Kolkata]]\n[[Category:Movie channels in India]]\n[[Category:Viacom 18]]\n[[Category:Television channels and stations established in 2019]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox TV channel\n| name            = Colors Bangla Cinema\n| logofile        = Logo_of_Colors_Bangla_Cinema.jpg\n| logosize        =150px \n| logoalt         = \n| launch          = {{Launch date|df=yes|2019|2|}} \n| owner           =[[Viacom 18]]\n| slogan          = \n| network         = \n| key people      = \n| share           = \n| share as of     = \n| share source    = \n| headquarters    = [[Kolkata]], [[Bengal]], [[India]]\n| country         = [[India]]\n| picture format  = \n| sister names    = \n{{Collapsible list\n| list_style      = text-align:left;\n| 1               = [[Colors Cineplex]]<br />[[Colors Cineplex HD]]<br />[[Colors (TV channel)|Colors]]<br />[[ETV Marathi|Colors Marathi]]<br />[[ETV Gujarati|Colors Gujarati]]<br />[[ETV Bangla|Colors Bangla]]<br /> [[ETV Kannada|Colors Kannada]]<br />[[ETV Odia|Colors Odia]]<br />[[Nickelodeon India|Nick]]<br />[[Nick Jr India|Nick Jr]]<br />[[Teen Nick India|Teen Nick]]<br />[[Sonic-Nickelodeon]]<br />[[MTV India]]<br />[[Colors Infinity]]<br />[[Colors Rishtey]]<br />[[Comedy Central India]]<br />[[MTV Beats]]<br />[[VH1 India]]<br />[[Colors Super